node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Austin Evans on June 14, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, laptop, screen and indoor.

node.text:
Ok this is a cool one: not only does Razer have a new smaller Blade 14 but it’s FINALLY gone AMD with a Ryzen 9 5900HX and RTX 3060/3070/3080 options. 

I’ve only been able to test a prototype so far but I really like this size/performance sweet spot.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Austin Evans on June 14, 2021. May be a closeup of 1 person.

node.text:
Been rocking the new Beats Studio Buds for the last week, for $150 they deliver solid, punchy sound and a really comfy fit. 

Downsides are no wireless charging and ANC is just ok compared to AirPods Pro. Still though these are probably going to stay in my pocket for a while, mostly because I just like the sound hah
